------------------------------
Release procedure for Krecipes
------------------------------

1. Update the version in krecipes_version.h
2. Prepare the tarball with releaseme.rb
   https://quickgit.kde.org/?p=releaseme.git
   * Use the kdelibs4 branch
   * Adjust the settings in the 'krecipesrc' file and do
     user@host:~/kde-devel/releaseme$ ./krecipes.rb
3. Upload the tarball to KDE's ftp
4. Upload the tarball to sourceforge
5. Open a bug for the KDE sysadmins to add the new version to bugs.kde.org
6. Announce the release in kde-apps.org
7. Mail about the release to:
   - krecipes-devel@kde.org
   - release-team@kde.org
